'''六硼化鍶'''（[[化學式|化學式]]：{{化學式|鍶|硼|6}}）室溫下為黑色晶狀粉末，非常穩定，熔點高，密度大。<ref name = msds >{{Cite web |url=http://www.espimetals.com/msds%27s/strontiumboride.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060209075029/http://www.espimetals.com/msds%27s/strontiumboride.pdf |archive-date=2006-02-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在最近的測試中，表現出的輕微半透明暗紅色晶體可以刮花[[石英|石英]]。<ref name=furnace>Moissan, Henri. The Electric Furnace.</ref>儘管不易于中毒，但對人體[[皮膚|皮膚]]、[[眼|眼]]和[[呼吸道|呼吸道]]都有刺激性。<ref name="msds"/>

== 磁性 ==

六硼化鍶和其他[[鹼土金屬|鹼土金屬]]硼化物一樣，在低溫下會展示出弱磁性。<ref>D. P. Young, D. Hall, M. E. Torelli, Z. Fisk, J. L. Sarrao, J. D. Thompson,
H. R. Ott, S. B. Oseroff, R. G. Goodrich, and R. Zysler. High-temperature weak ferromagnetism in a low-density free-electron gas. Nature (London), 397, 412 (1999).
</ref>這種情況被認為是晶格中有些雜質造成的，<ref>Shang, S., & Liu, Z. Thermodynamics of the B–Ca, B–Sr, and B–Ba systems: Applications for the fabrications of CaB6, SrB6, and BaB6 thin films. Applied Physics Letters, 2007, 90, 091914-1. Retrieved April 30, 2009, doi:10.1063/1.2710081</ref><ref>J. L. Gavilano, B. Ambrosini, H. R. Ott, D. P. Young, Z. Fisk, Low-temperature NMR studies of SrB6, Physica B: Condensed Matter, Volumes 281-282, 1 June 2000, Pages 428-429, ISSN 0921-4526, DOI: 10.1016/S0921-4526(99)01197-7 (http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/B6TVH-400WKV6-68/2/9b3bc29604aac16dd96856e9c7aab187)</ref>儘管其他解釋也必須。<ref> Dorneles, L., Venkatesan, M., Moliner, M., Lunney, J., & Coey, J. Magnetism in thin films of CaB6 and SrB6. Applied Physics Letters, 2004, 85, 6377-6379. Retrieved April 30, 2009, doi:10.1063/1.1840113</ref>六硼化鍶低溫下也用於對[[半導體|半導體]]性質的檢測。<ref>H. R. Ott, M. Chernikov, E. Felder, L. Degiorgi, E. G. Moshopoulou, J. L. Sarrao, Z. Fisk. Structure and low temperature properties of SrB6. Z. Phys. B, 1997, 102, 337-345.</ref>

== 製備 ==

在[[亨利·莫瓦桑|亨利·莫瓦桑]]的《電爐》一書中提到一種早期合成六硼化鍶的方法：在電爐中將[[硼酸鍶|硼酸鍶]]，[[鋁|鋁]]和[[碳|碳]]混合。<ref name="furnace"/>或者在固相體系下，真空電爐中2mol[[碳酸鍶|碳酸鍶]]，3mol[[碳化硼|碳化硼]]和1mol碳粉反應也可製備六硼化鍶。<ref name=reaction>Shu-Qi Zheng, Zeng-Da Zou, Guang-Hui Min, Hua-Shun Yu, Jian-De Han, Wei-Ti Wang. Synthesis of strontium hexaboride powder by the reaction of strontium carbonate with boron carbide and carbon. Journal of Materials Science Letters, 2002, 21, 313-315.</ref>

== 用途 ==

六硼化鍶可用作隔熱材料和[[核反應|核反應]]的[[控制棒|控制棒]]。<ref name="reaction"/>另一種用途現正在申請專利：飛行器在透明的[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]層使用SrB<sub>6</sub>納米粒。這種納米粒子的紅外線吸收特性可阻止紅外線的傳送而不阻礙可見光的傳播。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://appft1.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&Sect2=HITOFF&d=PG01&p=1&u=/netahtml/PTO/srchnum.html&r=1&f=G&l=50&s1=%2720090093578%27.PGNR.&OS=DN/20090093578&RS=DN/20090093578| title = United States Patent Application 20090093578| accessdate = 2009-05-05| archive-date = 2019-09-12| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190912180345/http://appft1.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&Sect2=HITOFF&d=PG01&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsrchnum.html&r=1&f=G&l=50&s1=%2720090093578%27.PGNR.&OS=DN%2F20090093578&RS=DN%2F20090093578}}</ref>

